name: Didus Phasianus
description:
--Fig.20--
Didus Phasianus is a magical creature from Elger, an exoplanet located 98 light years from Earth, orbiting the star Monch.
Didusses are celestial beings that have immense psychic strenghts and emanate high frequences of harmony wherever they are. In a planet where there's a Didus living in, flowers, plants and animals bloom instants after they touch Didus aura. They have power to control some celestial bodies in the path of evolution and can live up how many years they want to, as they have control of all cells in their body.
